the 36-hour period ending at 4 p.m. Wednesday. Oct. 1 is the beginning of the 
official rain year. 04,22,15,14,17 Rainfall Rainfall Normal rainfall Location 
last 36 hours since Oct. 1 to date Camarillo 0.01 10.20 12.80 Casitas Dam 0.08 
15.64 22.76 El Rio 0.03 11.08 14.63 Fillmore 0.23 12.00 18.20 Moorpark 0.09 
10.53 14.31 Ojai .05 12.64 20.83 Upper Ojai 0.05 15.03 22.94 Oxnard 0.09 11.64 
14.14 Piru 0.12 10.26 16.75 Santa Paula 0.14 13.24 16.99 Simi Valley 0.16 10.45 
