 Trabuco Hills 13 1/3, Fullerton 7 2/3 -- Joey Trainer won in No. 1 singles, 
6-2, 6-3, 6-2, for Trabuco Hills. Trabuco Hills (14-6) will play Los Alamitos 
in the second round today. Fullerton finishes 12-10. 
