Bishop Amat, 1-0. . . Lakewood has beaten Division I power Los Alamitos, 8-3. . 
. Dogged by injuries most of the season, Los Altos -- the third entry from the 
Miramonte League -- was healthy for its final game against Wilson and beat the 
Wildcats, 2-1. At the time, Wilson was ranked fifth in the state. 
</P>
