electronic news.Because of the huge amounts of data that can be sent over 
coaxial cables, data can be transferred to personal computers as much as 1,000 
times faster than today's fastest modems can transmit over the cable 
infrastructure. Intel said Tele-Communications Inc. and Rogers Cablesystems of 
