<HEADLINE>
<P>
CHILDREN: AGENCY SEEKS FOSTER HOMES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Vista del Mar Child & Family Services of West Los Angeles is looking for 
foster homes for children 5 and younger. 
</P>
<P>
 The agency pays for foster children's room and board, clothing and health 
care. If interested, call Joan Apt at (310) 836-1223, Ext. 280. 
</P>
<P>
 "Foster parents can be single or married, with or without children of their 
own," said Elias Lefferman of Vista del Mar. "Love for kids and room in the 
home for a child is what we look for." 
</P>
</TEXT>
