<DOCNO> LA051994-0360 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 043336 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
May 19, 1994, Thursday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
